name: Manav Seva Sansthan, Odisha
briefDescription: MANAV SEVA SANSTHAN is a voluntary organization came in to exist in the year 2018, by a group of women activist and youths , in particular women from marginalized & unprivileged backgrounds have the benefit of complete citizenship, earn with dignity and generate wealth and value for all. We are professional women headed organization working across religious and social divides to enable resource poor women to empower themselves i.e the socio â€“ economic and political empowerment of working women in rural areas in Angul District of Odisha, India. We particularly work with women and children of marginalized communities like Dalits, Scheduled Caste and Scheduled Tribes
